title: YouTube : most watched Latin artists ' music videos 2019
summary: This bar chart has 8 columns on the x axis representing Music Video, and Number of views in billions in each Music Video on the y axis.

The maximum Number of views in billions 6.33 is found at Music Video Luis Fonsi - Despacito ft. Daddy Yankee and the minimum is found at Nicky Jam x J. Balvin - X (EQUIS)  Video Oficial  Prod. Afro Bros & Jeon where Music Video is 1.68.
The difference of Number of views in billions between the highest and lowest Music Video is 4.65.
